OL,3,CBusinesses destroyed in fire
OL,4,Cdetermined to carry on
OL,6,FTwo businesses, gutted when flames
OL,7,Ftore through multiple shops and flats
OL,8,Fin Petersfield, have now reopened less
OL,9,Fthan three weeks after the devastating
OL,10,Ffire.
OL,12,FThe owners of an independent bookshop
OL,13,Fand a beauty salon have found new
OL,14,Fpremises and say they couldn't have
OL,15,Fdone it without the support of
OL,16,Feveryone in the community.
OL,18,FTim O'Kelly opened his bookshop on
OL,19,FLavant Street 30 years ago and says
OL,20,Fit's been very upsetting to see it
OL,21,Fdestroyed.
