OL,3,CBusinesses destroyed in fire
OL,4,Cdetermined to carry on
OL,6,F"It's been huge but having said that,
OL,7,Fnobody was hurt and only buildings and
OL,8,Fbooks and things got damaged, so we
OL,9,Fthank our lucky stars for that."
OL,11,FHe's managed to find a small temporary
OL,12,Fpremises on nearby Chapel Street and
OL,13,Fsays they're now "ready and raring to
OL,14,Fgo".
OL,16,F"We're in a bit of a shoebox here but
OL,17,Fit's fantastic, we've fit in so many
OL,18,Fbooks.
