OL,3,CBusinesses destroyed in fire
OL,4,Cdetermined to carry on
OL,6,F"We've managed to rescue quite a lot
OL,7,Fof the books, salvaged them from the
OL,8,Fshop. There was a lot of water damage
OL,9,Fbut some of them escaped."
OL,11,FHe hopes they will eventually be able
OL,12,Fto move back to the original shop once
OL,13,Fthe roof is replaced.
OL,15,FIt's nearly three weeks since the row
OL,16,Fof shops was devastated by the blaze
OL,17,Fthat ripped through the terraced
OL,18,Fbuilding, leaving the roof destroyed
OL,19,Fand the businesses below smoke and
OL,20,Fwater damaged, as firefighters battled
OL,21,Fto put out the flames.
