OL,3,CBusinesses destroyed in fire
OL,4,Cdetermined to carry on
OL,6,FThe One Tree bookshop isn't the only
OL,7,Fbusiness already back on its feet. The
OL,8,FHouse of Boo hairdressers and beauty
OL,9,Fsalon has also found new premises at
OL,10,Fthe bottom of town.
OL,12,FBut recent events have taken a huge
OL,13,Ftoll.J"It's been absolutely
OL,14,Fdevastating, I don't even have the
OL,15,Fwords," said salon owner, Rebecca
OL,16,FHallam, "I've lost everything, we all
OL,17,Fhave."
