OL,3,CBusinesses destroyed in fire
OL,4,Cdetermined to carry on
OL,6,F"I think it's affected us all in
OL,7,Fdifferent ways but we will get through
OL,8,Fit. We're going to pull together and
OL,9,Fwe will carry on."
OL,11,FThe fire is understood to have been
OL,12,Fstarted by an electrical overload, but
OL,13,Fthe cause of that is under
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FBusinesses say they are determined to
OL,17,Fbuild back better and continue to
OL,18,Fserve the communities that have
OL,19,Frallied to help them get through the
OL,20,Ftoughest of times.
